Pinnacle Point Needs $37 Million, Considers Rights Offer, Business Rescue

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-01T05:13:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/pinnacle-point-needs-37-million-considers-rights-offer-business-rescue.html
Pinnacle Point Group Ltd. (PNG)  said it
needs about 250 million rand to replace banking facilities and
to meet working capital requirements.  Amongst the initiatives the group is considering is a
rights offer and a business rescue for “certain group
companies,” Pinnacle Point said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  